@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminUsername = lisi
@adminPassword = 123456

### 登录并保存管理员 token
# 说明：后面的订单管理接口需要 order:list / order:update / order:delete 权限。
# 如果 lisi 不是管理员，请把上面的账号改成拥有这些权限的用户。
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.token); %}

### 创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "amount": 99.90,
  "remark": "HTTP Client 创建订单"
}

### 查询我的订单
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 管理员查询全部订单
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - 默认第一页，每页 10 条
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - 第 1 页，每页 10 条
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - 第 2 页，每页 5 条
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - 按状态筛选
# status: 0=待支付，1=已支付，2=已发货，3=已完成，4=已取消
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - pageNum/pageSize 小于 1 时使用默认值
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=0&pageSize=0
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - pageSize 超过 100 时自动按 100 处理
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=1000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 分页查询订单 - 非法状态，预期返回 code=400
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&status=9
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 未登录访问分页接口，预期返回 code=401
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 修改订单状态
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": 1
}

### 修改订单状态 - 非法状态，预期返回 code=400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": 9
}

### 删除订单
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
